  <title translate="true">MT-POP-Motions with Dwell Segments-DRDR</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Motions with Dwell Segments<keyword translate="true">DRD</keyword><keyword translate="true">DRDR</keyword><keyword translate="true">DRRD</keyword><keyword translate="true">RR</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="width:450px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Traditional Motion with Dwell Segments</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Motions with one or more </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwell</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> segment before and/or after </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Rise</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> or </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Return</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> segments are frequently used with industrial cams. Acronyms for the common motions are:</text></para>
          <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">DRD</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> - a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwell</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, then a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Rise</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> (or </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Return</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">), then a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwell</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> (an indexing motion)</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">DRDR</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> - &#160;a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwell</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, then a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Rise</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, then a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwell</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, then a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Return.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">DRRD</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> - a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwell</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> then a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Rise</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, then a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Return</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">, then a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwell</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">RR</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;" translate="true"> - a continuous sequence of </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Rise</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Returns</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;" translate="true">, no </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Dwells.</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Note</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> : a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Rise-Return</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> motion is often a quick turnaround; the motion is &#160;called a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Throw</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
